---
import GlobalFooter from '../components/GlobalFooter.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <title>AI CMO Advisor | Treetop Growth Strategy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Get a competitive analysis and 90-day marketing roadmap built on real CMO judgment. $99 starter report powered by live Ahrefs data and 10 years of growth strategy." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/ai-cmo-advisor" />
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/ai-cmo-advisor" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="AI CMO Advisor | Treetop Growth Strategy" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="$99 competitive analysis and 90-day roadmap. Real CMO judgment at AI speed." />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/og/ai-cmo-advisor.png" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="Treetop Growth Strategy" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/og/ai-cmo-advisor.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="AI CMO Advisor | Treetop Growth Strategy" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="$99 competitive analysis and 90-day roadmap. Real CMO judgment at AI speed." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[
    {"@type":"Product","name":"AI CMO Advisor","description":"Competitive analysis and 90-day marketing roadmap built on real CMO judgment, powered by live Ahrefs data.","url":"https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/ai-cmo-advisor","brand":{"@type":"Brand","name":"Treetop Growth Strategy"},"offers":[{"@type":"Offer","price":"99","priceCurrency":"USD","availability":"https://schema.org/InStock","description":"Starter Report: one-time competitive analysis and 90-day roadmap"},{"@type":"Offer","price":"249","priceCurrency":"USD","availability":"https://schema.org/InStock","description":"Monitor: monthly competitive refresh and what-changed memo"},{"@type":"Offer","price":"999","priceCurrency":"USD","availability":"https://schema.org/InStock","description":"Guided: monthly working call, deeper analysis, we shape your assets"},{"@type":"Offer","price":"2500","priceCurrency":"USD","availability":"https://schema.org/InStock","description":"Embedded: a part-time CMO who produces the work with you"}]},
    {"@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Is this a tool or does someone actually review my situation?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Both. The report is generated by Claude using your onboarding data and live Ahrefs data pulled for your specific competitors. Bill Colbert designed the system prompt and reviews every report before delivery. You get AI speed with real CMO judgment behind the framework."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"What is in the $99 report?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A competitive position snapshot comparing your organic authority to up to 3 competitors, a keyword gap analysis, a content positioning diagnosis, the top 3 growth levers for a company at your stage, and a 90-day priority roadmap. Plus a specific first-moves section written from the perspective of a CMO who has read your full situation."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"How is this different from Okara or other AI marketing tools?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Those tools draft content for you to post. This tells you what your marketing strategy should actually be. You use a content drafting tool when you know what to create. You use this when you need to figure out what to prioritize in the first place."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"What do the monthly plans deliver?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The ladder climbs from the $99 report. Monitor ($249/mo) keeps your competitive data refreshed monthly with a what-changed memo and a priority question answered. Guided ($999/mo) adds a monthly working call and asset help. Embedded ($2,500/mo) is a part-time CMO who produces the work with you. Enterprise is a custom AI-native GTM build."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"What kind of company is this built for?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Best fit: B2B companies with $500k to $10M in revenue that have some marketing motion but have hit a ceiling. You have a website, some content, probably some leads. You are not sure which channel to push harder, what your competitors are doing, or whether your positioning is working."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"How long until I get my report?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Within 24 hours of completing the onboarding questionnaire. Most come in same-day."}}
    ]}
  ]}
  </script>

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: #050D05; color: #F0FFF0; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 50; background: rgba(5,13,5,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2.5rem; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .nav-logo { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #F0FFF0; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(240,255,240,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link:hover { color: #F0FFF0; }
    .btn-p { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: #00C853; color: #050D05; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
    .btn-p:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
    .btn-p:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }
    .btn-g { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: transparent; color: #F0FFF0; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; cursor: pointer; }
    .lbl { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #00C853; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: block; }
    .sec-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

    /* Hero */
    .hero { padding: 9rem 2.5rem 5rem; }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero-h { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.07; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .hero-h em { font-style: italic; color: #00C853; }
    .hero-sub { font-size: 1.08rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.78; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 640px; }
    .email-row { display: flex; gap: 0; max-width: 520px; }
    .email-input { flex: 1; background: rgba(240,255,240,0.05); border: 1px solid #2A4A2A; border-right: none; padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem; color: #F0FFF0; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
    .email-input:focus { border-color: rgba(0,200,83,0.5); }
    .email-input::placeholder { color: #4A6A4A; }
    .trust-note { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #4A6A4A; margin-top: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .trust-note span { color: #00C853; }
    #signup-success { display: none; background: rgba(0,200,83,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,83,0.25); padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; max-width: 520px; }
    .success-h { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .success-p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.6; }
    #err-msg { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E0A0A0; margin-top: 0.6rem; }

    /* Sections */
    section { padding: 5rem 2.5rem; border-top: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .h2 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .h2 em { font-style: italic; color: #00C853; }
    .section-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

    /* Distinction */
    .distinction-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5px; background: #1A3A1A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; max-width: 820px; }
    .distinction-col { background: #050D05; padding: 2rem 2.25rem; }
    .distinction-col.them { background: #080F08; }
    .distinction-label { font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .distinction-label.them { color: #4A6A4A; }
    .distinction-label.us { color: #00C853; }
    .distinction-item { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.55; }
    .distinction-icon { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .distinction-icon.them { color: #2A4A2A; }
    .distinction-icon.us { color: #00C853; }

    /* Steps */
    .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5px; background: #1A3A1A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .step { background: #050D05; padding: 2rem 1.75rem; }
    .step-num { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 3rem; color: rgba(0,200,83,0.2); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .step-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .step-body { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* Report items */
    .report-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: #1A3A1A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; max-width: 820px; }
    .report-item { background: #050D05; padding: 1.75rem 2rem; }
    .report-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .report-title { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .report-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* Pricing */
    .pricing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5px; background: #1A3A1A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; max-width: 820px; }
    .price-card { background: #050D05; padding: 2.25rem 2.25rem; }
    .price-card.featured { background: #071407; }
    .price-tag { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; color: #F0FFF0; line-height: 1; margin: 0.75rem 0 0.25rem; }
    .price-cadence { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #8FAF8F; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .price-name { font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #00C853; }
    .price-desc { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .price-features { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-features li { font-size: 0.84rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.6; padding: 0.35rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #0F2A0F; display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .price-features li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .price-features li::before { content: "✓"; color: #00C853; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-list { max-width: 720px; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #1A3A1A; padding: 1.5rem 0; }
    .faq-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .faq-q { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: #F0FFF0; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .faq-q .faq-arrow { color: #00C853; font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform 0.2s; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .faq-q.open .faq-arrow { transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .faq-a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #C0D8C0; line-height: 1.8; max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.2s; }
    .faq-a.open { max-height: 400px; padding-top: 1rem; }

    /* CTA section */
    .cta-box { background: #0A1A0A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .cta-h { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 400; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.15; }
    .cta-sub { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8FAF8F; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.65; }
    .cta-form { display: flex; gap: 0; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto; }

    /* Proof bar */
    .proof-bar { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; padding: 1.75rem 2.5rem; border-top: 1px solid #1A3A1A; border-bottom: 1px solid #1A3A1A; background: #070F07; }
    .proof-item { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8FAF8F; display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; }
    .proof-item span:first-child { color: #00C853; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { padding: 7.5rem 1.5rem 3.5rem; }
      section { padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; }
      .distinction-grid, .steps, .report-grid, .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .email-row { flex-direction: column; max-width: 100%; }
      .email-input { border-right: 1px solid #2A4A2A; border-bottom: none; }
      .hide-mob { display: none !important; }
      .cta-form { flex-direction: column; }
      .proof-bar { gap: 1.25rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Treetop</a>
    <div class="hide-mob" style="display:flex;gap:2rem;align-items:center;">
      <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="nav-link">AI CMO Advisor</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="nav-link">Pricing</a>
      <a href="/resources" class="nav-link">Resources</a>
      <a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#pricing" class="btn-p" style="padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.78rem;">See pricing &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="lbl">AI CMO Advisor</span>
    <h1 class="hero-h">The AI CMO built on<br/><em>a real CMO's judgment.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Most AI marketing tools draft content for you to post. This diagnoses your marketing strategy. Submit your email, answer 7 questions about your business, and get a competitive analysis and 90-day priority roadmap within 24 hours.</p>

    <div id="signup-form">
      <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;top:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;" aria-hidden="true">
        <label for="hp-hero">Leave this empty</label>
        <input type="text" id="hp-hero" name="hp" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
      </div>
      <div class="email-row">
        <input class="email-input" type="email" id="hero-email" placeholder="you@yourcompany.com" autocomplete="email" />
        <button class="btn-p" id="hero-btn" onclick="submitHero()" style="white-space:nowrap;">Get my CMO report &rarr;</button>
      </div>
      <input class="email-input" type="text" id="hero-website" placeholder="yourcompany.com (optional, helps us research you)" autocomplete="url" style="margin-top:0.5rem;border-right:1px solid #2A4A2A;width:100%;max-width:520px;display:block;" />
      <p id="err-msg" style="display:none;"></p>
      <p class="trust-note"><span>&#10003;</span> No credit card. We verify your email before spending any AI on your situation.</p>
    </div>

    <div id="signup-success">
      <div class="success-h">Check your inbox.</div>
      <p class="success-p">We sent a verification link to <strong id="sent-to"></strong>. Click it to continue to your onboarding questionnaire. Takes about 10 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Proof bar -->
<div class="proof-bar">
  <div class="proof-item"><span>&#10003;</span> Built on 10+ years of CMO and growth strategy work</div>
  <div class="proof-item"><span>&#10003;</span> Live Ahrefs competitive data on every report</div>
  <div class="proof-item"><span>&#10003;</span> 24-hour delivery</div>
  <div class="proof-item"><span>&#10003;</span> $99 to start, cancel anytime</div>
</div>

<!-- The distinction -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">Why this is different</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Tools draft content.<br/>This <em>delivers strategy.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">There is no shortage of AI tools that will write LinkedIn posts or suggest keywords. The hard problem is knowing what to prioritize in the first place. That is what this solves.</p>
    <div class="distinction-grid">
      <div class="distinction-col them">
        <div class="distinction-label them">Other AI marketing tools</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon them">&#9632;</span> Draft content for you to approve and post</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon them">&#9632;</span> Suggest keywords based on generic data</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon them">&#9632;</span> Automate what you tell them to automate</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon them">&#9632;</span> Give you more output, not more direction</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon them">&#9632;</span> Assume you already know what to work on</div>
      </div>
      <div class="distinction-col">
        <div class="distinction-label us">AI CMO Advisor</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon us">&#10003;</span> Reads your competitive position with live Ahrefs data</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon us">&#10003;</span> Identifies the specific gaps and opportunities for your company</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon us">&#10003;</span> Tells you what to prioritize and in what order</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon us">&#10003;</span> Gives you a 90-day roadmap, not a content calendar</div>
        <div class="distinction-item"><span class="distinction-icon us">&#10003;</span> Starts with the strategic question, not the output</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">How it works</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Three steps.<br/>One clear <em>decision.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">From your first email to a report in your inbox, the whole process is designed to take less than 10 minutes of your time.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-title">Verify your email</div>
        <div class="step-body">Submit your email above. We send a verification link. Click it. No AI time gets spent until you confirm you are a real person with a real business problem.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-title">Answer 7 questions</div>
        <div class="step-body">What does your company do, who are your customers, who are your competitors, what channels are you using, and where are you stuck. Takes about 10 minutes. This is how the report becomes specific to you.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-title">Get your report</div>
        <div class="step-body">Within 24 hours, we pull live Ahrefs data on your competitors, run the full analysis, and deliver a report with a competitive snapshot, gap analysis, and a 90-day roadmap. Most come in same-day.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What is in the report -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">What you get</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Six things you will have<br/>that you <em>do not have now.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">Every report is built on your specific onboarding answers and live competitive data. Nothing is generic.</p>
    <div class="report-grid">
      <div class="report-item">
        <div class="report-icon" style="color:#00C853;">&#9632;</div>
        <div class="report-title">Competitive position snapshot</div>
        <div class="report-desc">Live Ahrefs data on up to 3 competitors you name. Domain authority, organic traffic, top pages. You will see exactly where you stand.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="report-item">
        <div class="report-icon" style="color:#00C853;">&#9632;</div>
        <div class="report-title">Keyword gap analysis</div>
        <div class="report-desc">The specific high-value terms your competitors rank for that you do not. Prioritized by traffic potential and competitive difficulty.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="report-item">
        <div class="report-icon" style="color:#00C853;">&#9632;</div>
        <div class="report-title">Content positioning diagnosis</div>
        <div class="report-desc">Where your messaging is and is not matching buyer intent. Specific pages and topics that need work, and why.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="report-item">
        <div class="report-icon" style="color:#00C853;">&#9632;</div>
        <div class="report-title">Top 3 growth levers</div>
        <div class="report-desc">The three things that would move the needle most for a company at your stage and competitive position. Not a list of 20 things. Three.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="report-item">
        <div class="report-icon" style="color:#00C853;">&#9632;</div>
        <div class="report-title">90-day priority roadmap</div>
        <div class="report-desc">What to focus on in month 1, month 2, and month 3. Sequenced so each month builds on the last. Clear, opinionated, actionable.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="report-item">
        <div class="report-icon" style="color:#00C853;">&#9632;</div>
        <div class="report-title">"What I would do next"</div>
        <div class="report-desc">The specific first move I would make as your CMO. Written after reading your full onboarding and all the data. This is the section most people read first.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Pricing -->
<section id="pricing">
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">Pricing</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Start with the report.<br/><em>Stay for the strategy.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">The $99 report is the right starting point. Get the analysis, see if the thinking resonates, and decide from there.</p>
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-name">Starter Report</div>
        <div class="price-tag">$99</div>
        <div class="price-cadence">One-time. No subscription required.</div>
        <div class="price-desc">The full competitive analysis and 90-day roadmap, built specifically for your business. Delivered within 24 hours.</div>
        <ul class="price-features">
          <li>Competitive position snapshot (up to 3 competitors)</li>
          <li>Keyword gap analysis with Ahrefs data</li>
          <li>Content positioning diagnosis</li>
          <li>Top 3 growth levers for your stage</li>
          <li>90-day priority roadmap</li>
          <li>"What I would do next" section</li>
          <li>Delivered within 24 hours</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#signup-form" class="btn-g" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;" onclick="document.getElementById('hero-email').focus()">Get my report &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card featured">
